Package: washoku
Title: Extra 'recipes' for Japanese Text, Date and Address Processing
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Shinya",
           family = "Uryu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "suika1127@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0493-6186"))
Description: In order to handle Japanese text in the feature engineering 
  process, morphological analysis is necessary. Following the framework of 
  `recipes`, to provide steps that can be applied to `textrecipes` for 
  subsequent processing.
